 1- mn kl qlwbnạ nhtf lyswʿ .. dh ḥbybnạ ạlgẖạly wmkẖlṣnạ wạbn ạllh
 wḥyạtnạ tnạdy mjdaⁿạ lyswʿ .. nsẖhd ʿn rb wfạdy bmwth whbnạ ḥyạẗ
 ạlqrạr- mjdaⁿạ lmlknạ ạlrb yswʿ rb ạlwjwd .. nhtf lfạdynạ bạ̉gẖạnynạ wʿlynạ yswd
 (wnfrḥ qlbh wnʿly mjdh .. dh mạt ʿlsẖạnạ wystḥq kl sjwd)2
 2- wbkl ậlạtnạ nqdm tsbyḥ .. ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlạ̉lḥạn bṣnwj wdfwf wbʿwd wrbạb
 wkmạn ạ̉ṣwạtnạ tʿly ạlmsyḥ .. whyfrḥ lmạ nsẖydnạ yldẖdẖ qlb ạlậb
 3- wạlsmạ nmlạhạ tsbyḥ lyswʿ .. trnymẗ jdydẗ llkẖrwf lyh ạlslṭạn
 nhdy lh krạmẗ wnsjd bkẖsẖwʿ .. wtmjd ạsmh kl kẖlyqẗ wkl lsạn</lyrics>
